Limits have to be set for each currency. 0 means you won't be able to deposit in this currency. Due to the nature of cryptocurrencies, deposit limits are not possible to enforce. If you want to limit your gambling we recommend a wager or loss limit.

Your account can be set with deposit limits. This setting limits the amount you can deposit per day, week or month. The limit becomes effective straight away. Canceling the deposit limit will take 24 Hours to process. Once the limit is hit, you will receive the email notification.
